{"word":"ξενίζω","slug":"ξενίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ξενίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ξένος\">ξένος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘be hospitable to’, <b>entertain <a href='B:510 10:23'>Ac 10:23</a>; <a href='B:510 28:7'>28:7</a>; <a href='B:650 13:2'>Hb 13:2</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b>receive hospitality, lodge, stay</b> as guest <b><a href='B:510 10:6'>Ac 10:6</a>, <a href='B:510 10:18'>18</a>, <a href='B:510 10:32'>32</a>; <a href='B:510 21:16'>21:16</a>; <a href='B:530 16:19'>1 Cor 16:19</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘surprise through strangeness of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>’, <b>amaze, surprise <a href='B:510 17:20'>Ac 17:20</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b>be surprised <a href='B:670 4:4'>1 Pt 4:4</a>, <a href='B:670 4:12'>12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ξενία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ξενοδοχέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}